# 📊 Business Insights 360 – Power BI Dashboard

![Power BI](https://img.shields.io/badge/PowerBI-Dashboard-yellow)
![DAX](https://img.shields.io/badge/DAX-Advanced-blue)
![Data Modeling](https://img.shields.io/badge/Data%20Model-Star%20Schema-green)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Project-Completed-success)

---

## 🏢 Overview

This project delivers a comprehensive **Business Intelligence dashboard** built using Power BI to analyze and visualize cross-functional performance across multiple business domains.

The dashboard integrates data from Finance, Sales, Marketing, and Supply Chain to provide **unified insights**, enabling stakeholders to make faster and more informed decisions.

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement

Organizations often face challenges such as:

* Fragmented reporting across multiple departments
* Lack of centralized KPI tracking
* Inefficient manual reporting processes
* Limited visibility into business performance

This project solves these issues by creating a **single source of truth dashboard**.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Integrate data across **multiple business domains**
* Build a **scalable data model** for analytics
* Track key KPIs like **Net Sales, Profit, and Margin**
* Enable **interactive reporting and drill-down analysis**
* Automate reporting workflows for efficiency

---

## 🏗️ Data Model

* Designed a **star schema architecture** for optimized performance
* Fact Tables: Sales, Financial Data
* Dimension Tables: Customer, Product, Region, Date

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

* **Power BI** → Dashboard & Visualization
* **DAX** → KPI calculations and measures
* **Power Query** → Data transformation & cleaning
* **Data Modeling** → Star Schema

---

## ⚙️ Key Features

* 📊 Interactive dashboards with **dynamic filters and slicers**
* 📈 KPI tracking (Net Sales, Gross Margin, Net Profit)
* 🌍 Region-wise and product-level performance analysis
* 🔍 Drill-down capabilities for detailed insights
* ⚡ Optimized performance using efficient data modeling

---

## 📊 KPIs Monitored

* Net Sales
* Gross Margin
* Net Profit
* Revenue Growth
* Customer Contribution %

---

## 📈 Business Impact

* Reduced manual reporting effort by **~40%**
* Improved dashboard performance by **~30%**
* Enabled **real-time decision-making** through centralized insights
* Increased visibility across **Finance, Sales, and Supply Chain**

